name: Login Feature
description:
In Order to perform successful login
  As a User
  I have to enter correct username and password

children.name: User should navigate to login page successfully
Given I am on homepage
When I click on login link
Then I should navigate to login page successfully
Verify error message while using invalid credentials
children.description:

children.name: Verify error message while using invalid credentials
Given I am on homepage
When I click on login link
And I enter email "abcd123@gmail.com"
And I enter password "xyz123"
And I click on login button

Then I should see the error message "Login was unsuccessful. Please correct the errors and try again.
No customer account found"

And I click on login button
Then I should login successfully
Verify that user should be able to logout successfully

And I enter password "prime123"
And I click on login button
And I click on logout link
Then I should be able to logout successfully
Verify user should navigate to register page successfully
Given I am on homepage
When I click on register link
Then I should be able to navigate to Register page showing "Register" text
Verify that first name, last name, email, password and confirm password fields are mandatory
Given I am on homepage
When I click on register link
And I click on register button
Then I should be able to see error messages at mandatory fields
Verify that user should create account successfully
Given I am on homepage
When I click on register link
And I select gender as "Female"
And I enter first name as "Gaurav"
And I enter last name as "Patel"
And I select day as "10"
And I select month as "March"
And I select year as "1990"
And I enter new email "abc123@abc.com"
And I enter password as "abcd1234#"
And I enter confirm password as "abcd1234#"
And I click on register button
Then I should be registered successfully with message "Your registration completed"
